<div id="review_3468209029" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3468209029" />
    <a title="Goran Đurić" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32747264-goran-uri"><img alt="Goran Đurić" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3468209029?book_show_action=true">Jul 29, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Goran Đurić" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Goran Đurić" href="/user/show/32747264-goran-uri">Goran Đurić</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3468209029" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10475375275121793080">Incessant ramblings uttered by schizophrenics with ADD in a dreamworld. The non sequiturs can be funny at times but it gets quite droning when a character or the narrator starts a monologue... and that happens quite often. It&apos;s an unfinished work that should be acknowledged for its originality, but the lack of polish is not something you can disregard. Avoid if at all possible.</span>
  <span id="freeText10475375275121793080" style="display:none">Incessant ramblings uttered by schizophrenics with ADD in a dreamworld. The non sequiturs can be funny at times but it gets quite droning when a character or the narrator starts a monologue... and that happens quite often. It's an unfinished work that should be acknowledged for its originality, but the lack of polish is not something you can disregard. Avoid if at all possible.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10475375275121793080" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


